OL,3,CFootage from inside Gaza shows mass
OL,4,Cgraves as thousands remain unidentified
OL,6,FEach nameless body is buried with a
OL,7,Funique code, in the hope that they
OL,8,Fmight be identified in the future, as
OL,9,FITV News
OL,11,FThousands of Palestinians killed in
OL,12,Fthe war in Gaza remain under the
OL,13,Frubble or unidentified in mass graves,
OL,14,Fdespite the fragile ceasefire with
OL,15,FIsrael.
OL,17,FAcross the entire territory, there are
OL,18,Fstill only two excavators that can be
OL,19,Fused to recover the dead, according to
OL,20,Fthe Red Cross.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
