OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779408177
OL,3,CFootage from inside Gaza shows mass
OL,4,Cgraves as thousands remain unidentified
OL,6,FIt means that more than two and a half
OL,7,Fyears into the war, many bodies have
OL,8,Fdecomposed beyond recognition, leaving
OL,9,Fthose missing loved ones still
OL,10,Fdesperately searching for answers.
OL,12,FBut with no DNA testing equipment in
OL,13,FGaza, its ten forensic medicine
OL,14,Fspecialists have little to go on.
OL,16,FInstead, the authorities have had to
OL,17,Fset up mass graves on the few bits of
OL,18,Fspare land available. With breeze
OL,19,Fblocks instead of headstones and
OL,20,Fnumbers where names should be, they
OL,21,Flook nothing like cemeteries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
