PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779408177
OL,3,CFootage from inside Gaza shows mass
OL,4,Cgraves as thousands remain unidentified
OL,6,FBut each nameless body is buried with
OL,7,Fa unique code, in the hope that they
OL,8,Fmight be identified in the future.
OL,10,FAbout 8,000 bodies are believed to
OL,11,Fstill be buried under debris
OL,12,Fthroughout Gaza, according to Gaza's
OL,13,Fhealth ministry.
OL,15,FIt estimates that more than 73, 000
OL,16,FPalestinians were killed during the
OL,17,Fwar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
