CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779408177
OL,3,CFootage from inside Gaza shows mass
OL,4,Cgraves as thousands remain unidentified
OL,6,FIn the chaos of Gaza, which lies
OL,7,Flargely in ruins after years of
OL,8,FIsraeli bombardment, it is a
OL,9,Fremarkable effort to bring some kind
OL,10,Fof order.
OL,12,FBut it offers little comfort to the
OL,13,Ffamilies of the missing, with the
OL,14,FPalestine Reporting Lab estimating
OL,15,Fthat there are still more than 14,000
OL,16,Fpeople unaccounted for.
OL,18,FSome have disappeared into Israel's
OL,19,Fdetention centres, more remain under
OL,20,Fthe rubble, but the fate of many
OL,21,Fremains unknown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
