PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779408177
OL,3,CFootage from inside Gaza shows mass
OL,4,Cgraves as thousands remain unidentified
OL,6,FAmong them are two of Um Yousef's
OL,7,Fsons. Her eldest, Yousef, was killed
OL,8,Fin an Israeli airstrike, but she says
OL,9,Fhis younger brothers, Firas and Jihad,
OL,10,Fjust disappeared.
OL,12,FUm Yousef insists her sons had no
OL,13,Fconnection to any armed group - Jihad
OL,14,Fwas only 16 and looks even younger in
OL,15,Fthe photo she has on her phone.
OL,17,FIsrael won't let international
OL,18,Freporters into Gaza, but Um Yousef
OL,19,Ftold our local camera crew she just
OL,20,Fwants answers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
