PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779408177
OL,3,CFootage from inside Gaza shows mass
OL,4,Cgraves as thousands remain unidentified
OL,6,F"To this day, I keep searching for his
OL,7,Fbody among the dead," she said. "I
OL,8,Ftell myself I would rather find him
OL,9,Fdead than continue not knowing his
OL,10,Ffate."
OL,12,FBut there are too many families left
OL,13,Fin limbo and not enough help.
OL,15,FIyad Abu Jred leads the Civil Defence
OL,16,Fteam in Gaza, tasked with sifting
OL,17,Fthrough the seemingly endless rubble.
OL,19,FHe says he gets more than ten calls a
OL,20,Fday from bereaved families begging for
OL,21,Fhis help. But the job is impossible.
