OL,3,CFootage from inside Gaza shows mass
OL,4,Cgraves as thousands remain unidentified
OL,6,F"My civil defence team doesn't have a
OL,7,Fsingle excavator," he said.
OL,9,F"We depend on the Red Cross to give us
OL,10,Fa few hours with their excavator so
OL,11,Fthat we can recover bodies."
OL,13,FThe Israeli authorities told ITV News:
OL,14,F"The State of Israel allows and
OL,15,Ffacilitates the entry of medical
OL,16,Fequipment in cooperation with aid
OL,17,Forganisations and the international
OL,18,Fcommunity..."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@RO]qD@AOUvD@AOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
