CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779408177
OL,3,CFootage from inside Gaza shows mass
OL,4,Cgraves as thousands remain unidentified
OL,6,F"We further clarify that when it comes
OL,7,Fto equipment defined as dual-use
OL,8,Fitems, Israel exercises extra caution
OL,9,Fand offers international organisations
OL,10,Falternative solutions that enable a
OL,11,Fhumanitarian response while preventing
OL,12,Fthe Hamas terrorist organisation from
OL,13,Fcynically exploiting the aid for its
OL,14,Fmilitary buildup."
OL,16,FBut the shortage of vital equipment
OL,17,Fleaves families denied both answers
OL,18,Fabout the fate of their loved ones and
OL,19,Fthe right to say goodbye.
OL,21,FIt is agony for those left behind.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
